	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Question : is there a way to get a converted image that isn't "shaky" ?
<br />I just hate how shaky the resluting NES ROMs are, I understand you want this effect to add more colors but it really looks terrible on my computer.
<br />
<br />PS : Also, is there a way to prepare the images for conversions without using a pay-ware (fotshop) ? Because the results looks horrible if I don't prepare them for conversion.

		

		</td>
